# ORM Layer Rules
- ORM files should be created only under folder 'backend/orm', backend directory is relative to project root folder.
- ORM Model files should be created under folder 'backend/orm/model'.
- ORM should only perform database operations; no business logic should exist here.
- Cursor AI should use SQLAlchemy for ORM mapping.
- ORM layer should support CRUD operations for the tables in Database